REGULAR SIMPLEX INSCRIBED IN n-CUBE:
Possible when a Hadamard matrix of order n+1 exists.

   n  Hadamard?   V(simplex)/V(cube)   Corner pieces
   1        YES                    1               0
   2         no                  1/2               1
   3        YES                  1/3               4
   4         no                  N/A             N/A
   5         no                  N/A             N/A
   6         no                  N/A             N/A
   7        YES                  N/A             N/A
   8         no                  N/A             N/A

